OL,3,CItaly investigates church painting of
OL,4,Cangel restored to look like Giorgia
OL,5,CMeloni
OL,7,FItaly's culture minister has launched
OL,8,Fan investigation into the
OL,9,Freconstruction of a church painting,
OL,10,Fafter claims it has been made to
OL,11,Fresemble Italian Prime Minister
OL,12,FGiorgia Meloni.
OL,14,FThe artwork in the Basilica of San
OL,15,FLorenzo in Lucina, Rome, originally
OL,16,Fshowed two angels surrounding a marble
OL,17,Fstatue of Umberto II, Italy's last
OL,18,Fking.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
