OL,3,CItaly investigates church painting of
OL,4,Cangel restored to look like Giorgia
OL,5,CMeloni
OL,7,FBut recent restoration works appear to
OL,8,Fshow one of the angels with "a
OL,9,Ffamiliar, astonishingly contemporary
OL,10,Fface", as first reported by the
OL,11,FItalian newspaper La Repubblica.
OL,13,FIn an announcement on Saturday, the
OL,14,FMinistry of Culture announced they
OL,15,Fwill now launch an investigation "to
OL,16,Fascertain the nature of the
OL,17,Fintervention carried out on the
OL,18,Fcontemporary painting contained in one
OL,19,Fof the chapels of San Lorenzo in
OL,20,FLucina and decide what to do next".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
