OL,7,FCultural heritage law in Italy rules
OL,8,Fthat restorations on protected sites
OL,9,Fmust be approved by the
OL,10,FSuperintendency of Archaeology, Fine
OL,11,FArts, and Landscape - the state
OL,12,Fauthority responsible for protecting
OL,13,Fcultural heritage.
OL,15,FGiorgia Meloni has reacted to the
OL,16,Fcontroversy herself. She posted a
OL,17,Fphotograph of the angel on her
OL,18,FInstagram, writing: "No, I definitely
OL,19,Fdon't look like an angel", adding a
OL,20,Flaughing emoji.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
