OL,3,CItaly investigates church painting of
OL,4,Cangel restored to look like Giorgia
OL,5,CMeloni
OL,7,FCarolina Morace from the Five Star
OL,8,FMovement, a political party in Italy,
OL,9,Ftold ITV News: "This is absurd,
OL,10,Funworthy and culturally disturbing.
OL,12,F"This is neither satire nor conceptual
OL,13,Fart: it is an affront to art history,
OL,14,Fto institutional decorum, and to the
OL,15,Fcredibility of those entrusted with
OL,16,Fsafeguarding Italy's cultural heritage.
OL,18,F"It is not culture; it is propaganda.
OL,19,FAnd it damages Italy's reputation
OL,20,Fabroad."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
