OL,7,FThe restoration work was completed by
OL,8,FBruno Valentinetti after the chapel
OL,9,Fcontaining the painting was affected
OL,10,Fby water damage.
OL,12,FValentinetti has denied that he
OL,13,Fintended to immortalise Meloni,
OL,14,Fclaiming he only restored the image of
OL,15,Fthe original fresco.
